{"tid":1802618,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史高斯：紅魔鋒線媲美歐洲列強","createTime":"2019-12-29T15:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T16:54:11.000Z","uid":31626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce3710df78b1d25f9ec4ad42feb4df7e7f20b8c","tid":1802618,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯名宿史高斯向來要求高，但盛讚現時鋒線已經可以跟一眾歐洲強隊相並論。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯在周六英超對般尼一役，以馬斯亞、華舒福、丹尼爾占士組成三叉戟，結果憑前兩者建功以2:0作客勝出。史高斯（Paul Scholes）說：「前線3子可以媲美歐洲列強的鋒線。」<br />\n<br />\n「馬斯亞、華舒福都能夠衝擊防線，占士亦非常出眾，還有美臣格連活後備入替。」史高斯又指，普巴只要作戰態度正選，有足夠專注力，是世界最佳中場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，史高斯表示紅魔現時除了鋒線及普巴之外，其他的都不夠好：「我一直聽到有人說曼聯欠穩定性，因為他們年輕，但其實已經不太年輕了。」雖然如此，他仍然認為曼聯今季至少需要殺入前4。"},{"pid":"e8842b30ccb2358d57811cbfdcdaaecaefc9ef5f","tid":1802618,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"條撚樣依排咁搶口？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81a59ad60aab7c932150da0ac2938dac057011b","tid":1802618,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa591ba68de4d64c98f0211e3c8f8fdca929f24","tid":1802618,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:19:36.000Z","msg":"個頭唔尖都叫戟？"},{"pid":"e428307ae69627fb1b061176aab6b5b7c5d94a2c","tid":1802618,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"識波"},{"pid":"daf3527057cdd87019170ced6fb36e3660f1e72d","tid":1802618,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"收爹啦"},{"pid":"7f2ac9d0dc1f37efeebe881c8fe150162e67cb3f","tid":1802618,"uid":50873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6fa591ba68de4d64c98f0211e3c8f8fdca929f24","tid":1802618,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r